{"componentChunkName":"component---node-modules-gatsby-theme-portfolio-minimal-src-templates-article-index-tsx","path":"/my-first-article/python/python9/","result":{"pageContext":{"article":{"banner":{"alt":"파이썬 기초","caption":"Photo by <u><a href=\"https://unsplash.com/photos/Nc5Q_CEcY44\">Google</a></u>","src":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/png;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/b87af/pythonlogo.png","srcSet":"/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/ea049/pythonlogo.png 125w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/bf58b/pythonlogo.png 250w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/b87af/pythonlogo.png 500w","sizes":"(min-width: 500px) 500px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/df328/pythonlogo.webp 125w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/2d2c6/pythonlogo.webp 250w,\n/static/fe2007ff5fefc27a884eb9773510900b/01f4a/pythonlogo.webp 500w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 500px) 500px, 100vw"}]},"width":660,"height":399.96}}}},"body":"<h2>try/except</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>try :\n<ul>\n<li>로직, 기능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>except &#x3C;오류종류> :\n<ul>\n<li>try문에서 오류가 발생할때, 실행</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">try</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  a_err <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token builtin\">int</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'안녕'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>a_err<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">except</span> ValueError <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f'오류 메세지: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">오류 메세지: invalid literal for int() with base 10: '안녕'</code></pre></div>\n<h2>try/except/else/finallytry :</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>try :\n<ul>\n<li>로직, 기능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>except &#x3C;오류종류> :\n<ul>\n<li>try문에서 오류가 발생할때, 실행</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>else :\n<ul>\n<li>try문이 성공할 때 발생</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>finally :\n<ul>\n<li>try문의 결과와 상관없이 실행</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>assert</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>조건이 False일 때, 발생하는 에러</li>\n<li>디버깅 모드에서만 작동하지만, 파이썬은 기본 디버깅 모드임</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">8</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 참이므로 assert는 실행 X</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">assert</span> a_int <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2의 배수가 아닙니다.\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2의 배수입니다.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">2의 배수입니다.</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\">a_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">7</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 거짓이므로 assert가 실행 됬다.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">assert</span> a_int <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"2의 배수가 아닙니다.\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2의 배수입니다.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nAssertionError                            Traceback (most recent call last)\n\nc:\\python\\gigit_2\\day3.ipynb Cell 52 line 3\n      &lt;a href='vscode-notebook-cell:/c%3A/python/gigit_2/day3.ipynb#Y111sZmlsZQ%3D%3D?line=0'>1&lt;/a> a_int = 7\n----> &lt;a href='vscode-notebook-cell:/c%3A/python/gigit_2/day3.ipynb#Y111sZmlsZQ%3D%3D?line=2'>3&lt;/a> assert a_int % 2 == 0, \"2의 배수가 아닙니다.\"\n      &lt;a href='vscode-notebook-cell:/c%3A/python/gigit_2/day3.ipynb#Y111sZmlsZQ%3D%3D?line=4'>5&lt;/a> print('2의 배수입니다.')\n\n\nAssertionError: 2의 배수가 아닙니다.</code></pre></div>\n<h3>raise error</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">try</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    a_int <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">487</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> a_int <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">4</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># 지금 if문이 참이므로 밑에 exception이 실행 된거임</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\"># 만약 거짓일 경우엔 밑에 \"4의 배수입니다.\"가 프린트 된다.</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">raise</span> Exception<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"4의 배수가 아닙니다.\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'4의 배수입니다.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">except</span> Exception <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> e <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f'에러메세지:</span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">에러메세지:4의 배수가 아닙니다.</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>지금 if문이 참이므로 밑에 exception이 실행 된거임</li>\n<li>만약 거짓일 경우엔 밑에 \"4의 배수입니다.\"가 프린트 된다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Exception 만들어서 적용하기</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">NotThreeMultipleError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Exception<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">def</span> <span class=\"token function\">__init__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>self<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> error_msg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token builtin\">super</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>__init__<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>error_msg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"python\"><pre class=\"language-python\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">try</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span> <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">raise</span> NotThreeMultipleError<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'3의 배수가 아닙니다.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'3의 배수 입니다.'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">except</span> Exception <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string-interpolation\"><span class=\"token string\">f'오류명: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token builtin\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\"> / 오류 메세지: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token string\">'</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n     </code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">오류명: &lt;class '__main__.NotThreeMultipleError'> / 오류 메세지: 3의 배수가 아닙니다.</code></pre></div>","categories":["Python","기초"],"date":"October 14, 2023","description":"파이썬 기초","id":"88d2da62-f0fb-526b-8eb0-0b42f1f7dabb","keywords":["Python","기초","예외처리"],"slug":"/my-first-article/python/python9/","title":"[파이썬 기초] 예외처리","readingTime":{"text":"3 min read"}},"listingPagePath":"/blog"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3262260831","948380417"],"slicesMap":{}}